Author: ComputerGenie 游놊游낖游닉#7004
Content:
```#!/bin/bash
file="$HOME/StakedNotary/peer_ips.txt"
while IFS= read -r line
do
    ip=$( echo $line )
    echo "$ip"
    if [ ${#ip} -gt 1 ]; then
    CFEKMYLO=$(komodo-cli -ac_name=CFEKMYLO addnode $ip onetry)
    CFEKMYLO6=$(komodo-cli -ac_name=CFEKMYLO6 addnode $ip onetry)
    fi
done <"$file"
```
